  'batana-oil-true-soap-bar', 'FMT-BO-SB', 'Batana Oil True Soap Bar', 'Batana Oil', 'Elaeis oleifera',
  'InStock', 'Concentrated & Artisanal', '["batana oil soap","true soap bar","handmade soap","artisan soap","Miskito","La Mosquitia","Honduras","natural soap","hair soap","body wash","shampoo bar","saponified batana oil"]', '["Jabón de Batana","Batana Soap","Jabón de Aceite de Ojon","Miskito Artisan Soap","True Soap Bar"]', 'Handmade artisanal Miskito batana oil soap from wild Elaeis oleifera kernels in La Mosquitia. A daily wash for soft hair and skin, rooted in traditional care.',
  '{"handler":"batana-oil-true-soap-bar","productGroupId":"FMT-BO-SB","catalog":"Batana Oil","category":"Health & Beauty > Hair Care","brand":"Forestal MT","name":"Batana Oil True Soap Bar","qualityBadge":"Concentrated & Artisanal","item":4,"botanical":"Elaeis oleifera","material":"palm kernel","ingredients":"Saponified batana oil, natural glycerin, plant-based oils, purified water, natural fragrance","origin":"Made in Honduras","storage":"Store in a cool, dry, and dark place. Always keep tightly sealed. Avoid prolonged heat and humidity.","shelfLife":"For best potency, use within 12–18 months.","shipping":"Worldwide via DHL Express","shortDescription":"Handmade artisanal Miskito batana oil soap from wild Elaeis oleifera kernels in La Mosquitia. A daily wash for soft hair and skin, rooted in traditional care.","description":"An artisanal cleansing bar rooted in Miskito tradition. Handcrafted with 100% saponified Batana Oil from wild Elaeis oleifera palm kernels of La Mosquitia, Honduras, this true soap offers gentle, nourishing cleansing for hair, skin, and body. Unlike commercial detergent bars, this is genuine soap made through traditional saponification — preserving the natural glycerin and skin-loving properties of pure Batana Oil. Used for generations by Miskito families as an all-in-one wash, it cleanses without stripping natural moisture. From rainforest to ritual, each bar carries ancestral wisdom into modern self-care.","commonNames":["Jabón de Batana","Batana Soap","Jabón de Aceite de Ojon","Miskito Artisan Soap","True Soap Bar"],"traditionalUses":["Hair washing and conditioning","Body cleansing","Face washing","Hand soap","Shaving soap base","Travel-friendly all-in-one wash"],"howToUse":["Hair Wash: Wet hair thoroughly. Rub the soap bar directly onto scalp and hair in circular motions to create lather, or lather in hands first and apply to hair. Massage scalp for 1–2 minutes. Work lather through to ends. Rinse thoroughly with warm water. Follow with conditioner if desired. Use 2–3 times per week.","Body Wash: Wet skin in shower or bath. Lather soap between hands or use a washcloth. Apply lather to body, massaging gently. Rinse thoroughly. The natural glycerin will leave skin soft without residue.","Face Wash: Wet face with warm water. Lather soap in hands and apply gently to face in circular motions. Avoid eye area. Rinse thoroughly with cool water. Pat dry. Use morning and night.","Shaving: Wet skin with warm water. Lather soap generously on shaving area using a brush or hands. Shave as usual. Rinse thoroughly. The natural oils will provide glide and post-shave moisture.","Hand Soap: Keep at sink. Lather between hands with water. Rinse clean.","Extend Bar Life: After each use, place on a well-draining soap dish away from direct water spray. Allow to air dry completely between uses."],"processingMethod":["Oil Preparation — Authentic Batana Oil is sourced from Miskito harvesters who cold-press wild Elaeis oleifera kernels from La Mosquitia rainforest.","Lye Solution — A precise lye (sodium hydroxide) solution is prepared with purified water, measured for exact saponification ratios.","Saponification — Batana Oil is slowly heated and combined with lye solution. The mixture is stirred continuously as it saponifies (converts oil into soap and natural glycerin).","Supporting Oils — Additional plant-based oils are blended in to enhance lather, conditioning, and skin feel.","Molding — The thick soap mixture is poured into traditional molds and allowed to set for 24–48 hours.","Curing — Bars are removed from molds and cured in ventilated racks for 4–6 weeks. This aging process hardens the bars, completes saponification, and develops a mild, skin-friendly pH.","Trimming & Packaging — Cured bars are hand-trimmed, inspected for quality, and packaged in eco-friendly boxes."],"tags":["batana oil soap","true soap bar","handmade soap","artisan soap","Miskito","La Mosquitia","Honduras","natural soap","hair soap","body wash","shampoo bar","saponified batana oil"],"relatedProducts":["raw-batana-oil","batana-oil-hair-wash","batana-oil-hair-conditioner"],"audience":{"type":"PeopleAudience","suggestedGender":"unisex","suggestedMinAge":13},"disclaimer":"FOR TRADITIONAL USE ONLY. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease. Discontinue use if irritation occurs. Keep out of reach of children. Consult a healthcare professional before use if pregnant or nursing. Individual results may vary."}', '{"handler":"batana-oil-true-soap-bar","productGroupId":"FMT-BO-SB","catalog":"Batana Oil","image":{"url":"https://cdn.forestal-mt.com/products/productGroup/batana-oil-true-soap-bar.png","alt":"Batana Oil True Soap Bar - Forestal MT product image","caption":"Batana Oil True Soap Bar — Artisanal Miskito Soap from La Mosquitia, Honduras","width":1200,"height":1200,"encodingFormat":"image/png","creator":"Forestal Murillo Tejada S. de R.L.","uploadedDate":"2026-02-16"},"ogImage":{"url":"https://cdn.forestal-mt.com/products/og/batana-oil-true-soap-bar.png","alt":"Black box packaging of Forestal MT Batana Oil Soap Bar with gold lettering and palm nut icon","caption":"Batana Oil True Soap Bar - 100% saponified Elaeis oleifera kernel oil from La Mosquitia, Honduras (2.6 oz)","width":1200,"height":630,"encodingFormat":"image/png","creator":"Forestal Murillo Tejada S. de R.L.","uploadedDate":"2026-02-16"},"variantImages":[{"sku":"fmt-bo-sb-100-g","url":"https://cdn.forestal-mt.com/products/variants/batana-oil-true-soap-bar-100-g.png","alt":"Batana Oil True Soap Bar 100 g - Forestal MT","caption":"Batana Oil True Soap Bar from La Mosquitia - Artisanal - 100 g","width":1200,"height":1200,"encodingFormat":"image/png","creator":"Forestal Murillo Tejada S. de R.L.","uploadedDate":"2026-02-16"}]}', '{"handler":"batana-oil-true-soap-bar","catalog":"Batana Oil","productSlug":"batana-oil-true-soap-bar","seoTitle":"Handcrafted Miskito Batana Oil True Soap for Skin and Hair","seoDescription":"100% true-origin artisanal batana oil soap sourced from La Mosquitia, Honduras. Daily soap for soft hair, skin, and body care. Wholesale worldwide.","ogImageUrl":"https://cdn.forestal-mt.com/products/og/batana-oil-true-soap-bar.png","ogImageAlt":"Black box packaging of Forestal MT Batana Oil Soap Bar with gold lettering and palm nut icon","ogImageCaption":"Batana Oil True Soap Bar - 100% saponified Elaeis oleifera kernel oil from La Mosquitia, Honduras (2.6 oz)","ogImageWidth":1200,"ogImageHeight":630,"twitterCard":"summary_large_image","relatedProducts":"raw-batana-oil, batana-oil-hair-wash, batana-oil-hair-conditioner","published":true}'
