  'InStock', 'Raw & Traditional', '["jimerito stingless bee honey","stingless bee honey eye drops","jimerito eye health honey","melipona honey for eyes","raw jimerito honey","miel jimerito ojos","natural eye remedy honey","Honduras stingless bee honey","miel de jimerito tendencia","meliponini honey antioxidant","honey eye drop trend","bee honey cataract remedy"]', '["Miel de Melipona","Stingless Bee Honey","Xunan Kab","Mayan Honey"]', 'Raw Jimerito stingless bee honey from Honduras, revered in Mayan tradition and valued for energy, immune balance, skin vitality, and traditional eye support.',
  '{"handler":"jimerito","productGroupId":"FMT-SBH-JM","catalog":"Stingless Bee Honey","category":"Health & Beauty > Health Care","brand":"Forestal MT","name":"Jimerito","qualityBadge":"Raw & Traditional","item":5,"botanical":"Tetragonisca angustula","material":"jimerito bee","ingredients":"Traditional honey from stingless bees, naturally rich in antioxidants, enzymes, and minerals.","origin":"Made in Honduras","storage":"Store in a cool, dry, and dark place. Always keep tightly sealed. Avoid prolonged heat and humidity.","shelfLife":"For best potency, use within 12–18 months.","shipping":"Worldwide via DHL Express","shortDescription":"Raw Jimerito stingless bee honey from Honduras, revered in Mayan tradition and valued for energy, immune balance, skin vitality, and traditional eye support.","description":"A rare treasure from the stingless Tetragonisca angustula bees of Honduras. Jimerito honey is harvested from wild log hives in the biodiverse landscapes of Olancho, where indigenous communities have maintained ancestral beekeeping traditions for centuries. Unlike common honeybee honey, Jimerito is produced by tiny, gentle stingless bees known locally as \"Jimerito\" or \"Xunan Kab\" in Mayan culture. This raw, unfiltered honey carries a distinctive tangy-sweet flavor profile and watery consistency due to higher moisture content—a natural characteristic of meliponini honey. Revered in traditional medicine for eye health, immune support, and skin vitality, Jimerito has gained global attention as a natural remedy trending on social media. From the hands of local harvesters to your wellness routine, this honey bridges ancient wisdom with modern health-conscious living.","commonNames":["Miel de Melipona","Stingless Bee Honey","Xunan Kab","Mayan Honey"],"traditionalUses":["Boosts energy and immune defense","Promotes skin vitality","Traditional eye support","Gourmet uses and applications"],"howToUse":["For Eye Health (Traditional Use): Apply 1-2 drops of pure Jimerito honey directly into each eye before bedtime. Gently close eyes and allow the honey to spread naturally across the surface. May cause temporary mild stinging sensation. Use consistently for traditional eye health support. Always ensure hands and dropper are clean before application.","For Immune Support & Energy: Take 1 teaspoon of Jimerito honey 2-3 times daily, either directly or dissolved in lukewarm water or herbal tea. Consume on an empty stomach in the morning for optimal absorption, or between meals throughout the day. Do not heat above room temperature to preserve enzymatic properties.","For Respiratory Health: Mix 1 teaspoon of Jimerito honey in warm (not hot) water with fresh lemon juice. Sip slowly to soothe throat inflammation, ease congestion, and support respiratory function. Use 2-3 times daily during seasonal challenges.","For Wound Care & Skin Health: Apply a thin layer of Jimerito honey directly to clean, minor wounds, burns, or skin irritations. Cover with a clean bandage if desired. Reapply 1-2 times daily until healed. The honey''s antimicrobial properties support natural healing.","Storage Note: Keep refrigerated after opening. Due to high moisture content typical of stingless bee honey, proper storage preserves freshness and prevents fermentation."],"processingMethod":["Harvest selection — Careful selection of the honey chambers from wild log hives of Tetragonisca angustula.","Gentle extraction — Local harvesters use traditional, careful methods to remove the honey while protecting the colony.","Simple straining — The honey is lightly strained to remove larger pieces of wax.","Natural resting — The honey is allowed to rest so it keeps its natural texture.","Storage — The honey is stored in sealed containers, traditionally gourds or glass jars, to protect its natural character."],"tags":["jimerito stingless bee honey","stingless bee honey eye drops","jimerito eye health honey","melipona honey for eyes","raw jimerito honey","miel jimerito ojos","natural eye remedy honey","Honduras stingless bee honey","miel de jimerito tendencia","meliponini honey antioxidant","honey eye drop trend","bee honey cataract remedy"],"relatedProducts":["hibiscus-flowers","moringa-leaves","lemongrass","linden-tilia","nettle-leaves"],"audience":{"type":"PeopleAudience","suggestedGender":"unisex","suggestedMinAge":13},"disclaimer":"FOR TRADITIONAL USE ONLY. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease. Discontinue use if irritation occurs. Keep out of reach of children. Consult a healthcare professional before use if pregnant or nursing. Individual results may vary."}', '{"handler":"jimerito","productGroupId":"FMT-SBH-JM","catalog":"Stingless Bee Honey","image":{"url":"https://cdn.forestal-mt.com/products/productGroup/jimerito.png","alt":"Jimerito - Forestal MT product image","caption":"Jimerito — Raw Stingless Bee Honey from Olancho, Honduras","width":1200,"height":1200,"encodingFormat":"image/png","creator":"Forestal Murillo Tejada S. de R.L.","uploadedDate":"2026-02-16"},"ogImage":{"url":"https://cdn.forestal-mt.com/products/og/jimerito.png","alt":"Amber glass dropper bottle with beige label showing Jimerito Stingless Bee Honey from The Mayans Heritage","caption":"Jimerito - Pure stingless bee honey from Olancho, Honduras in 30ml amber dropper bottle, The Mayans Heritage","width":1200,"height":630,"encodingFormat":"image/png","creator":"Forestal Murillo Tejada S. de R.L.","uploadedDate":"2026-02-16"},"variantImages":[{"sku":"fmt-sbh-jm-30-ml","url":"https://cdn.forestal-mt.com/products/variants/jimerito-30-ml.png","alt":"Jimerito 30 ml - Forestal MT","caption":"Jimerito Melipona - Raw Stingless Bee Honey - 30 ml","width":1200,"height":1200,"encodingFormat":"image/png","creator":"Forestal Murillo Tejada S. de R.L.","uploadedDate":"2026-02-16"},{"sku":"fmt-sbh-jm-250-ml","url":"https://cdn.forestal-mt.com/products/variants/jimerito-250-ml.png","alt":"Jimerito 250 ml - Forestal MT","caption":"Jimerito 