  'OutOfStock', 'Wildcrafted & Shade-Dried', '["muicle herb wildcrafted","justicia spicigera dried","muicle tea","muicle herb herbal tea","traditional herb Honduras wildcrafted","muicle herb traditional uses","muicle herb healthy blood pressure levels","muicle herb antioxidant protection","justicia spicigera benefits"]', '["muicle"]', 'Muicle (Justicia spicigera), a Mesoamerican herb rooted in sacred tradition for blood vitality, feminine balance, and skin clarity.',
  '{"handler":"muicle-herb","productGroupId":"FMT-TH-MU","catalog":"Traditional Herbs","category":"Food, Beverages & Tobacco > Beverages > Tea & Infusions","brand":"Forestal MT","name":"Muicle Herb","qualityBadge":"Wildcrafted & Shade-Dried","item":29,"botanical":"Justicia spicigera","material":"whole plant","ingredients":"Shade-dried muicle, valued for its natural plant colorants and antioxidants.","origin":"Made in Honduras","storage":"Store in a cool, dry, and dark place. Always keep tightly sealed. Avoid prolonged heat and humidity.","shelfLife":"For best potency, use within 12–18 months.","shipping":"Worldwide via DHL Express","shortDescription":"Muicle (Justicia spicigera), a Mesoamerican herb rooted in sacred tradition for blood vitality, feminine balance, and skin clarity.","description":"The crimson-flowered plant Justicia spicigera, known as ''muicle'' or ''mohuite'' in Mesoamerican tradition, bleeds purple-red pigment when crushed, signaling its deep phytochemical richness. Wild-harvested from Honduras'' highland forests and traditional gardens, this herb carries Mexican and Central American indigenous knowledge about blood health and purification. \n\nRevered for its striking color and traditional women''s wellness applications, it is shade-dried to preserve its anthocyanin and flavonoid content. Offered in flowering tops and leaves, free from synthetic dyes or color enhancement.","commonNames":["muicle"],"traditionalUses":["Supports healthy blood pressure levels","Provides antioxidant protection","Promotes skin health and appearance","Aids urinary tract wellness"],"howToUse":["Herbal Infusion (Tea): Place 1-2 teaspoons (5-8g) of dried Muicle herb (leaves, stems, flowers) in a teapot or cup. Pour 1 cup (240ml) of boiling water over the herb. Cover and steep for 10-15 minutes. Strain and drink 1-3 cups daily.","For Blood Purification (Traditional Use): Drink 2-3 cups of Muicle tea daily as part of a traditional cleansing protocol. The deep purple infusion is traditionally used for blood purification and detoxification.","For Women''s Health: Consume Muicle tea 1-2 times daily to traditionally support menstrual regularity, ease menstrual discomfort, and promote reproductive wellness.","For Digestive & Intestinal Health: Drink 1 cup of Muicle tea after meals to support digestive comfort and traditional intestinal wellness.","Color Note: Muicle tea produces a beautiful deep purple to blue color, which intensifies with steeping time and changes with pH (adding lemon turns it pink)."],"processingMethod":["Selective Harvesting — Herbs are hand-picked at peak maturity, with care to protect plant populations and ecosystems.","Manual Cleaning — Unwanted parts like dirt and dry leaves are removed; useful portions are sorted for quality.","Drying Setup — Delicate herbs are tied in small bunches or spread thinly to allow natural airflow.","Shade Drying — Materials dry slowly in a cool, shaded space to preserve aroma, color, and beneficial properties.","Storage — Once fully dry, herbs are trimmed and sealed in airtight containers to maintain freshness and potency."],"tags":["muicle herb wildcrafted","justicia spicigera dried","muicle tea","muicle herb herbal tea","traditional herb Honduras wildcrafted","muicle herb traditional uses","muicle herb healthy blood pressure levels","muicle herb antioxidant protection","justicia spicigera benefits"],"relatedProducts":["snake-plant","blessed-holy-thistle","linden-tilia","sensitive-plant","leaf-of-life-miracle-leaf"],"audience":{"type":"PeopleAudience","suggestedGender":"unisex","suggestedMinAge":13},"disclaimer":"FOR TRADITIONAL USE ONLY. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease. Discontinue use if irritation occurs. Keep out of reach of children. Consult a healthcare professional before use if pregnant or nursing. Individual results may vary."}', '{"handler":"muicle-herb","productGroupId":"FMT-TH-MU","catalog":"Traditional Herbs","image":{"url":"htt